data.text:
Site URL: https://www.diabeticexchangeusa.com/

Hi, is it possible to create automated return shipping labels? For example, if a customer visits my website and inputs/submits their information on one of my forms, a USPS return label is automatically emailed to them? Amazon and pretty much every clothing website I have seen has this feature.
